      "widgets_values": [
        "An ultra-photorealistic, candid mirror selfie of a woman in her mid-20s with a messy bun, holding a sign that reads \"ZIT In Pixel Space!\" taken in a small, dimly lit bedroom at night. Shot on an iPhone 15 Pro with a 26mm lens.  The lighting is from a warm bedside lamp, creating soft shadows and gentle falloff into darker edges. The image should mimic raw iPhone realism with subtle grain and a candid snapshot feel. She is wearing a thin ribbed off-white tank top and light grey lounge shorts, with a relaxed posture and sleepy, faintly smiling expression. No filters, no plastic skin, no studio setup. "
